      <title>穆迪称美国债务动态“与 Aaa 评级不一致”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-debt-dynamics-inconsistent-with-a-triple-a-rating-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级在周二发布的一份报告中警告称，下一届美国政府“必须应对不断扩大的预算赤字”，而近一年前，该公司宣布对美国主权信用状况给出负面展望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-debt-dynamics-inconsistent-with-a-triple-a-rating-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 11:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
