      <title>刺激措施激发乐观情绪，欧洲依赖中国的行业激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/europe-s-china-reliant-sectors-surge-as-stimulus-fuels-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国北京宣布一揽子刺激措施以重振世界第二大经济体之后，因对中国经济放缓的担忧而备受关注的欧洲股市周二强劲上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/europe-s-china-reliant-sectors-surge-as-stimulus-fuels-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:54:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
